reviewText: it was not English dubbed as advertised
Great price, DVDs are new, plays flawless. Good series. Japanese with english subtitles. I didn't look if there was english dub, but I don't look for dub'd anime.

As advertised, it's quality was good. Since I knew this story Anime was as I expected. Home was much cuter than the comic. Original "blood of life" became "fire of life". I liked it more than the original comic but I want to watch stories to the end.

I made two mistakes when I bought this collection. It is the second of two sets and it is only available in Japanese with subtitles. I hate reading subtitles and my japanese language skills are limited. Maybe I will think better of it when my understanding of Japanese language improves.
